{
  "stem": "6016.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You got access to water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't live only on water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at least once a day food, I think we had, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, you didn't know who you were even.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in these conditions that we found ourselves, we did not think of-- of a Shabbat or religion or even-- maybe for-- from a-- as we used to say, God will help.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK, dear God, help us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Customarily, you say, oh-- or traditionally call it, help, help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we-- I personally didn't lose hope, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I see it now, maybe sustained me Bergen-Belsen was my attitude with my work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would say, maybe it's the Red Cross packages, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those were nice sandwiches, honey cake from the French that I got, that I could smuggle in between the [? waltzes ?] to-- to do my job.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Bergen-Belsen, I had no job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bergen-Belsen, I was unemployed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Monotonous, just laying around and thinking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever comes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever comes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, talking about songs, there was one-- in Neusalz, there was one that used to sing 'My Yiddishe Momme.'",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw her in Brazil.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's gone by now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Toska Blaunstein, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She really-- she was singing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of them tried to sing too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes, to make a little-- to lively up a little bit, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- [SINGING] My Yiddishe momme, this is a [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My Yiddishe momme, I wish if you would be here now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] I wish if my mother would live and to see, and survive, and to-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and to know what life is, to have a little joy, both my parents, and my brothers too.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember my father very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
